docs.abstract: Investment banks say underwriting for companies brings in more trading revenue and vice versa. Goldman’s performance suggests that’s not always the case.
docs.snippet: Investment banks say underwriting for companies brings in more trading revenue and vice versa. Goldman’s performance suggests that’s not always the case.
docs.lead_paragraph: Wall Street is putting a trading axiom to the test. Investment banks often say that underwriting debt and equity issues for companies brings in trading activity, and vice versa. The latest results from the country’s five big players — Bank of America, Citigroup, Goldman Sachs, JPMorgan and Morgan Stanley — show that that’s not necessarily the case.

headline.main: Link Between Underwriting and Trading Is Put to the Test

docs.abstract: Toronto is the only city outside the United States on Amazon’s list. Its mayor credited Canada’s open approach to immigration and strong support for education.
docs.snippet: Toronto is the only city outside the United States on Amazon’s list. Its mayor credited Canada’s open approach to immigration and strong support for education.
docs.lead_paragraph: OTTAWA — John Tory, the mayor of the only city outside the United States to make the list of 20 finalists for Amazon’s second headquarters displayed some typical Canadian modesty on Thursday. Toronto, Mr. Tory said, had only “made the playoffs.”

headline.main: Why Toronto Made ‘the Playoffs’ for Amazon’s Headquarters
headline.print_headline: Support for Education And Immigration Help Toronto Make the Cut

docs.abstract: Ms. Vega, who was most recently at CNN, succeeds John Hockenberry, who retired in August and was later accused of sexual harassment and bullying behavior.
docs.snippet: Ms. Vega, who was most recently at CNN, succeeds John Hockenberry, who retired in August and was later accused of sexual harassment and bullying behavior.
docs.lead_paragraph: Tanzina Vega has been named the new host of the public radio program “The Takeaway,” succeeding John Hockenberry, who retired in August and was subsequently accused of engaging in sexual harassment and bullying behavior during his decade with the show.

headline.main: Tanzina Vega Is New Host of WNYC’s ‘The Takeaway’

docs.abstract: The social network, which is overhauling what people consume on the site, said its business would remain robust even if some users spent less time on its platform.
docs.snippet: The social network, which is overhauling what people consume on the site, said its business would remain robust even if some users spent less time on its platform.
docs.lead_paragraph: SAN FRANCISCO — Mark Zuckerberg, Facebook’s chief executive, has embarked on an overhaul of what people see and consume on the social network. The changes have left investors wondering whether people will still spend as much time on the site and whether brands will continue placing as many digital ads there.

headline.main: Facebook Aims to Soothe Wall Street Over News Feed Changes
headline.print_headline: Facebook Chief Tries to Soothe Wall Street Over Changes to Site’s News Feed

docs.abstract: The wearable-camera maker styled itself a media company, but success is hard when the boss wastes time and resources chasing whims.
docs.snippet: The wearable-camera maker styled itself a media company, but success is hard when the boss wastes time and resources chasing whims.
docs.lead_paragraph: GoPro’s genius discount grows larger. The wearable-camera maker styled itself a media company when it went public in 2014, but even its hardware business is suffering job cuts as sales fall short. Success is even harder than usual when — as at Snap, which fancied itself a camera company — the boss wastes time and resources chasing whims.

headline.main: GoPro Needs to Know Its Limits

docs.abstract: “If you’re just putting in numbers and hoping for the best,” an accountant says, “then maybe you need a preparer.”
docs.snippet: “If you’re just putting in numbers and hoping for the best,” an accountant says, “then maybe you need a preparer.”
docs.lead_paragraph: If the thought of preparing your own tax return feels overwhelming — even with do-it-yourself software — there’s always the option of hiring a professional preparer.

headline.main: How Taxpayers Who Want Help Can Find a Reputable Preparer
headline.print_headline: How Taxpayers Seeking Help Can Find a Qualified Preparer

docs.abstract: A Super Bowl ad by Ram had viewers openly wondering whether the company really used Dr. King’s words about the value of service to sell vehicles.
docs.snippet: A Super Bowl ad by Ram had viewers openly wondering whether the company really used Dr. King’s words about the value of service to sell vehicles.
docs.lead_paragraph: The online blowback was swift for Ram on Sunday after the carmaker used a sermon given by the Rev. Dr. Martin Luther King Jr. as the voice-over for a Super Bowl ad.

headline.main: Ram Trucks Commercial With Martin Luther King Jr. Sermon Is Criticized

docs.abstract: The producer agreed to a $300 million Netflix deal months after Shonda Rhimes signed for $100 million and Apple and Amazon contributed to a manic market.
docs.snippet: The producer agreed to a $300 million Netflix deal months after Shonda Rhimes signed for $100 million and Apple and Amazon contributed to a manic market.
docs.lead_paragraph: The battle between the Hollywood establishment and the streaming-media giants has caused big changes in the entertainment industry in recent months, driving up the prices of major stars and series producers while leaving traditional companies in danger of losing relevance.

headline.main: As the Streaming Wars Heat Up, Ryan Murphy Cashes In
headline.print_headline: A Magnet For Talent Shakes Up Hollywood

docs.abstract: A top Morgan Stanley broker was repeatedly accused of violence against ex-wives and girlfriends. Bank managers were told. But he kept his job.
docs.snippet: A top Morgan Stanley broker was repeatedly accused of violence against ex-wives and girlfriends. Bank managers were told. But he kept his job.
docs.lead_paragraph: Over 15 years, four women in Lake Oswego, Ore., a wealthy Portland suburb, sought police protection against the same man, court filings show.

headline.main: Morgan Stanley Knew of a Star’s Alleged Abuse. He Still Works There.
headline.print_headline: A Rainmaker in Hot Water: ‘Everybody Knew’

docs.abstract: It couldn’t hail an Uber, answer a cooking question or learn music preferences. Here’s why it may not be the right time to buy Apple’s new smart speaker.
docs.snippet: It couldn’t hail an Uber, answer a cooking question or learn music preferences. Here’s why it may not be the right time to buy Apple’s new smart speaker.
docs.lead_paragraph: On my second day with Apple’s new HomePod, I asked the artificially intelligent speaker to play some music. Siri, the virtual assistant that powers HomePod, enthusiastically replied, “O.K., let’s get going with some Dashboard Confessional.”

headline.main: Apple’s HomePod Has Arrived. Don’t Rush to Buy It.
headline.print_headline: It Can’t Cook, Pick Songs or Get a Car, but It Sounds Nice
